# Netscape HTTP Cookie File
# Replace this with a real export from your browser if you need
# age-gated / login-required YouTube downloads.
#
# How to export:
#   1. Install the "Get cookies.txt LOCALLY" browser extension (Firefox/Chrome).
#   2. Sign in to YouTube in that browser.
#   3. Open YouTube, click the extension, export to file.
#   4. Save as cookies.txt at the path you set in COOKIES_FILE in .env.
#
# WARNING: this file is a session token. Keep it private.
